    {
        "content": "<p>OK, here are some notes, which I hope are legible (and correct!). <a href=\"/user_uploads/21317/tci79BkSzLnPjJe7V1mphTAQ/lattice_measures.pdf\">lattice_measures.pdf</a></p>",
